data.meta_description: Kip Moore has become one of the most promising newer artists in country music on the strength of his songwriting, singing and excellent live shows.  The Tifton, Ga...
data.text:
Kip Moore Will Remain One of the 'Wild Ones' ... for Now

There may be several love songs on Kip Moore's upcoming sophomore album Wild Ones (Aug. 21), but the 35-year-old isn't worried about settling down any time soon. Sorry, ladies!

Kip Moore, 'Wild Ones': Everything You Need to Know

Kip Moore’s Wild Ones is a commanding album. Its light on hooks and many songs aim for a higher common denominator. Listening to his second studio album is an investment, but it’s one that will pay off for most.

Win a Kip Moore Wet 'N Wild Trip to Orlando!

Kip Moore’s Wild Ones album hits stores and digital retailers on August 21, and the singer is hoping you’ll get wild with him. Enter here for a chance to win a trip to Wet ’n Wild in Orlando, Fla., this fall, including tickets to his show in Lake Buena Vista.

Kip Moore Teaming Up With Jewel in the Studio

It appears Kip Moore has been cooking up something in the studio lately with a buddy fans may recognize.

Kip Moore Unveils New Track from Wild Ones, 'Magic' [Listen]

In anticipation for the release of his new album Wild Ones on Aug. 21, Kip Moore has released the audio for a new song off the record called “Magic.” Moore says the track is almost an anti-love song, counter to the unrealistic portrayals of romance pervasive on the radio.

Kip Moore Headlining Labor Day Concert to Benefit Veterans

“I’m to Blame” singer Kip Moore has signed on to headline the Labor of Love Music Festival hosted by CASE Construction on Labor Day this year, which will benefit the Wounded Warrior Project and raise awareness about the need to hire veterans for skilled jobs in the construction and manufacturing industries.

Kip Moore Hitting the Road on Wild Ones Tour

Stay off the roads this fall, because Kip Moore is going wild! The country singer will embark the 2015 Wild Ones tour in October in support of his upcoming sophomore album.

Georgia's Hottest Country Singers, One Epic Photo

The Peach State’s four most swoon-worthy country exports — Cole Swindell, Kip Moore, Jason Aldean and Luke Bryan — may be attempting to break the internet.

Kip Moore Reveals Major Crush on Shania Twain

Shania Twain has been turning heads since her debut on the country music scene in the 1990s, and young star Kip Moore is apparently one of them. In an interview with Glamour magazine, Moore reveals just how deep his long-time crush on the iconic artist runs.
